reviewText: I'm a fan of a well built men and this guy is that. There's plenty of nudity and he looks good. However the film is boring, just a whole lot of standing or being shown how to pose by the very intrusive photographer - who even offers suggestions on how to shave! It fails to create any sense of excitemnt about the shoot or the model. 2 stars for the model, nothing for the film. Dont waste your money.
